overview:
Schumacher Cargo Logistics is an international moving and Automobile shipping company. Shipping overseas from the USA since 1977, we offer our clientele a level of customer service that exceeds your expectations. You can be confident that your goods or vehicle will arrive at their destinations in the same condition you handed them over to us. We have offices in Los Angeles, New York, Miami, Houston and Savannah. We are the leaders in industry innovation and offer our services with Honesty, Integrity and Value for money.
